Package hu.bme.mit.theta.solver.smtlib.dsl.gen

Class SMTLIBv2BaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.solver.smtlib.dsl.gen.SMTLIBv2BaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
SMTLIBv2Listener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class SMTLIBv2BaseListener extends Object implements SMTLIBv2Listener
This class provides an empty implementation of SMTLIBv2Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
